data.description: This is a 1950's ranch style house located on Garnet Mesa. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms and one full bath. The basement has 1 non-conforming bedroom, 3/4 bath, large family room, laundry and a workshop in the unfinished portion of the basement. Recent upgrades include new flooring in the kitchen, vinyl windows on the main floor, sewer line from the house to the street and new electric panel. The outside has a covered patio, garden beds and partially fenced backyard. There is a 1 car attached garage and 1 car carport. The schools are right around the corner bus picks up at the end of the driveway! Come check out this beautiful home!
